name: FinalSurviver
description: This is a game called Elf Survivor. In this game, you are going to fight as Elf wonderland. You can choose to be a Knight Elf or either a Wizard Elf, for the wizard elf you have to use the coin to unlock. When you can get coins by killing the enemies on the wonderland, and you can use coins to buy extra buff for your elf! Go fight and kill the Boss！
